Domin yawan girgizar ƙasa da ake yi a ƙasar, ƙasar ba ta da shiri sosai don magance matsalar.
Ko da yake an gina mafaka a Aceh don tsunami, ba a yawan samunsu a wasu yankunan da ke bakin teku.
