Kuma wannan shi ne yadda aka buga ƙwallo.
Rangers sun ba da kyauta kuma Livingston ya sami damar yin wasa tare da Declan Gallagher, Robinson da Menga, wanda ya kama kwallon kuma ya yi nasara a tsakiyar filin fansa.
A lokacin, Rangers sun fi rinjaye a kan kwallon amma ba su iya shiga cikin kariya ba, saboda haka kowa yana da kwanciyar hankali a filin wasan Liam Kelly.
Haka kuma a wasan na biyu, Alfredo Morelos ya tilasta wa Kelly ya kare raga a wani lokaci.
Mai tsaron ragar Rangers Allan McGregor ya yi nasara da Scott Pittman, kuma Lithgow ya yi fice a wasan gaba da Livingston.
