Shugaban ya yi magana a kaikaice game da nadin Kavanaugh, yayin da yake magana game da muhimmancin 'yancin zaben na Republican a lokacin zaben.
"Kwanaki biyar ne kawai suka rage kafin a yi wani babban zabe a rayuwarmu.
