"Tun da yake kasar Sin na kara shiga harkar kere kere, Amurka za ta ninka kudaden da take bayarwa don gudanar da bincike a wannan fannin", in ji Kai-Fu Lee, mai ba da tallafi da kuma masaniyar kere kere, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
An fitar da wannan bayani ne bayan da bangarori daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka suka yi maganganu game da AI, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabara ta musamman kan AI.
A daidai wannan lokacin, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirin ta na zama jagora a harkar bunkasa fasahar kere kere ta hanyar 2030 a shekarar da ta gabata.
"Haɗa kasafin kuɗin bincike na AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, la'akari da cewa sauran ƙasashe suna baya da Amurka kuma muna aiki don ci gaba na gaba a cikin AI", in ji Lee.
Karin kudade zai ninka yiwuwar cewa babbar nasarar da ake samu ta fasaha ta wucin gadi za ta kasance a Amurka, Lee ya fada a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa mai suna AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order, wanda Houghton Mifflin Harcourt ya wallafa a wannan watan, shi ne shugaban kamfanin Sinnovation Ventures, wanda ya samar da kudade ga daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kere kere na fasaha a kasar Sin, Face++.
A shekarun 1980s, ya yi aiki a Carnegie Mellon University a kan tsarin fasaha na wucin gadi wanda ya lashe kyautar mafi kyawun wasan kwaikwayo na Othello a Amurka. Daga baya ya kasance a kan kwamitin gudanarwa na Microsoft Research da kuma shugaban kamfanin Google na kasar Sin.
Lee ya amince da gasar fasahar gwamnatin Amurka da ta gabata kamar gasar Robotics Challenge ta Hukumar Bincike ta Ci Gaban Amurka (Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency) kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a yi gasar ta gaba don taimakawa gano masu mafarki na gaba.
"Masana kimiyya na Amurka suna bukatar su yi aiki tukuru domin samun tallafin gwamnati", in ji Lee.
"Ba kasar Sin ce ke daukar masu ilimi ba, kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, kamfanonin fasaha kamar su Facebook da Google sun yi amfani da manyan masana kimiyya daga jami'o'i don su yi aiki a kan ƙirar fasaha.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauyen da aka yi a kan manufofin shige da fice na iya taimaka wa Amurka wajen tallafa wa kokarin da ake yi na yin amfani da fasaha ta wucin gadi.
