"Gwamnatin kasar Sin ta kasafin kudi ga masu aikin kimiyya kamar yadda hukumar kimiyya ta kasar Sin da sauran hukumomin gwamnati ke ba da kudi ga masu binciken Amurka, amma ingancin aikin kimiyya a kasar Sin ya kasa", in ji Lee.
