Almanah: Wanda ya ƙirƙiri na'urar kirga abubuwa ta Geiger
Kuma yanzu shafi na mu na Almanah na safiyar Lahadi: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, yau shekara 136 da ta wuce, kuma a ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi Johannes Wilhelm Hans Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya ƙirƙira wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna rediyo, wannan ƙirar ta kai ga na'urar da ake kira Geiger counter.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, Geiger counter ya zama tushen al'adun gargajiya kamar a cikin fim din Coronado Clock na 1950 wanda ke nuna waɗannan masu binciken da ba su da tabbas Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan?"
Rogers:  Wannan shi ne Geiger counter da ake amfani da shi wajen gano ma'adanai masu aikin rediyo kamar uranium.
Idan ka saka waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin ƙarar atomatik da ke fitowa daga ma'adanai masu aikin rediyo.
Evans: "Kada ka gaya mini, wannan zai zama abin kunya!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ya cika shekara 63.
