Game da kursiyin da Kit Harington ya shahara ba ya yarda da mazaunin mutum
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin HBO mai rikitarwa na zamanin da na wasan kwaikwayo Game da Thrones.
Amma, ɗan wasan kwaikwayo, mai shekara 31, ya yi watsi da ra'ayin cewa jarumi mai zafin hali ne, yana cewa irin waɗannan ayyuka a kan allo suna nufin cewa matasa maza suna jin cewa dole ne su kasance masu tsauri.
Da yake magana da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya yi tunanin cewa wani abu ya ɓace kuma ya yi tambaya game da yadda za a magance matsalar ƙarancin maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri 'yar wasan Game of Thrones mai suna Rose Leslie, ya ce yana da "tabbataccen ra'ayi" cewa wannan matsalar tana bukatar kulawa.
"Ina jin cewa a wani wuri mun yi kuskure game da namiji", in ji shi.
Me muka koya wa maza yayin da suka girma game da matsalar da muke fuskanta yanzu?
Kit ya gaskata cewa, talabijin yana da alhakin yawan maza da suke nunawa.
Ya ci gaba: "Mene ne haihuwar jariri, kuma menene ake koyarwa?
Abin da ake koyarwa a talabijin da kuma a kan titi yana koya wa yara maza cewa dole ne su zama irin waɗannan idan suna son su zama maza.
Ina tsammanin wannan shine ainihin ɗayan manyan tambayoyin zamaninmu - yadda za a canza shi?
Domin a bayyane yake cewa akwai wani abu da ya faru da matasa.
A cikin hirar, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai taba shiga cikin wasan Game of Thrones ba bayan wasan ya ƙare a lokacin bazara, yana cewa yana kan "wurin da yaƙi da dawakai".
Tun daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai shiga cikin shirin Sam Shepard na True West, wanda ke ba da labarin wani mai shirya fim da ɗan'uwansa mai fashi.
A kwanan nan, ɗan wasan ya bayyana cewa yana ganin saduwa da matarsa Rose shine mafi kyawun abin da ya faru game da Game of Thrones.
"Na sadu da matata a wannan wasan kwaikwayon, don haka ya ba ni iyalina na gaba da rayuwata", in ji shi.
Rose ta taka rawar Ygritte a cikin kyautar Emmy, wanda ya kasance ƙaunataccen Jon Snow na Kit.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a cikin Yuni 2018 a gidan Leslie a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton ƙaruwar sababbin cututtuka da kashi 14%
Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Masana kiwon lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 suna fama da wannan ciwo.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an bayar da rahoton sabbin mutane kusan 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin shari'o'in sun samo asali ne daga jima'i, suna canja abin da ya gabata.
A wasu sassan kasar Sin, cutar HIV ta samo asali ne daga jini da aka yi wa mutane.
Amma, a wannan hanyar, an rage yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na ƙasar Sin a wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
A shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke da HIV da AIDS a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce ga al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An halatta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma ana zargin cewa ana nuna bambanci sosai ga mutanen LGBT.
Saboda ƙa'idodin da gwamnati ta kafa, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza suna yin aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna da alaƙa da rashin isasshen kariya ta jima'i a cikin irin waɗannan alaƙar.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta amince da amfani da maganin cutar HIV a ko'ina domin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa bayanan da aka fitar daga gidan majalisar dattijai na GOP sun kasance "karya ne mai hatsari" da kuma "ka'idojin da ake bukata".
A ranar Asabar, wakilin majalisar wakilai na Amurka Maxine Waters ta yi tir da zargin cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar wakilai uku na Republican a shafin Wikipedia.
'Yan Democrat na Los Angeles sun tabbatar da cewa 'yan adawa masu fafutukar nuna nuna bambanci da kuma shafukan yanar gizon su ne suke yada irin wannan zargi.
"Ƙarya, ƙarya, da kuma ƙarin ƙazantacciyar ƙarya", in ji Waters a cikin sanarwar Twitter.
An ce bayanin da aka buga ya ƙunshi adireshin gida da kuma lambobin waya na 'yan majalisar dattawa Lindsey Graham (South Carolina) da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch (duka daga Utah).
An wallafa wannan bayanin a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani mutum da ba a san shi ba ya wallafa a Capitol Hill, a lokacin da ake sauraron karar da majalisar dattawa ta yi game da zargin cin zarafin dan takarar shugaban kasa, Brett Kavanaugh.
An samu wannan bayanin ne jim kadan bayan da wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo na gargajiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ce adireshin IP ɗin da ke gano asalin aika-aikar yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma ya ba da bayanin memba na ma'aikacin Waters, in ji Hill.
"Wannan zargi da ba shi da tushe ba, karya ne kwarai da gaske", Waters ya ci gaba.
Ma'aikatanmu waɗanda ke da mutuntaka, bayanan sirri da aminci da ke cikin haɗari saboda waɗannan da'awar na yaudara da ƙarya ba su da alhakin wannan ɓarnar.
Wannan da'awar da ba ta da tushe ba ta zama gaskiya kuma ba za a iya musanta ta ba.
An yi ta sukar sanarwar da Waters ya yi a yanar gizo cikin sauri, ciki har da tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda ya samo asali ne daga fushi", in ji Fleischer.
Wannan ya nuna cewa yana da wani hali da bai dace da dan majalisa ba.
Idan aka zargi wani da abin da bai yi ba, kada su yi fushi.
Ba za su iya yin tsayayya ba.
Ba za su iya yin shakkar dalilin da ya sa ake tuhumar ba.
Dole ne su kasance masu kwanciyar hankali.
Fleischer ya yi kwatancen yadda Waters ya amsa sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa mai shari'a Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar suka zargi da nuna fushi a zaman kotun na ranar Alhamis.
Dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican Omar Navarro, wanda ke neman kujerar Waters a zaben fidda gwani, ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Babu matsala, idan gaskiya ne", ya yi ihu.
Waters ya ce a cikin sanarwar da ya bayar, ofishinsa ya gargadi hukumomin tsaro da na tsaro game da wannan zargin.
"Muna yin duk abin da za mu iya don gano masu laifin", ya ci gaba, "kuma a hukunta su saboda duk ayyukan da suka yi, wanda ke da lahani da kuma hadari ga dukkan ma'aikatana".
Hoton Johnny English Strikes Again - Ba a biya shi ba Rowan Atkinson ɗan leƙen asiri
A yau, ana neman ma'anar Brexit a duk wani sabon fim na Burtaniya, kuma wannan ya zama abin da ya dace musamman a cikin jerin wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English, wanda ya fara ne da Johnny English a 2003 kuma ya ci gaba da sake farfadowa da Johnny English a 2011.
Abin dariya ne a kan yadda muka kasance wawaye a kan sabon fitar da kayayyakin kasar?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English, mai idanu masu duhu da kuma rashin iyawa, ya sake samun izini ya yi abubuwa a hanyarsa ta yau da kullum - kuma wannan babban zane-zane na zane-zane yana nufin yankunan da ba su da harshen Turanci.
Hakika, wannan wani ɗan leƙen asiri ne, wanda duk da irin ƙazamar da'awar da yake da ita na yin fim, ya ɗan yi kama da Clouseau, ɗan ɗan yi kama da Mr. Bean, ɗan kuma kamar mutumin da ya sa waƙar "Chariots of Fire" a bikin buɗe wasannin Olympics na London na 2012.
Har ila yau, wannan hali ya dogara ne akan matafiyi da kuma Atkinson na duniya mai ban mamaki, wanda aka taɓa yin shi a cikin tallan talabijin na Barclaycard da aka manta, wanda ya bar abin da ya fi rikici.
Akwai wani abu ɗaya ko biyu da ya fi kyau a fim ɗin nan na ƙarshe.
Na ji daɗin ganin Johnny English yana zuwa cikin jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu, yana saka tufafinsa na ƙarfe na dā, kuma fuka-fukan jirgin sama suna ta motsawa a kan kwalkwali na ɗan lokaci.
An nuna baiwar Atkinson na yin wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri, amma abin dariya ya zama ba shi da mahimmanci kuma yana da ban mamaki, musamman idan manyan fina-finai na leken asiri kamar 007 da Mission Impossible suna ba da wasan kwaikwayo da kansu.
Kamar dai wannan abin dariya ya fi dacewa ga yara fiye da manya, kuma a gare ni, kasada ta Johnny English ba ta da hankali kamar yadda fim din Atkinson na Bean.
A yanzu, akwai zato cewa Birtaniya na cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin gidan yanar gizo na 'yan leken asiri na Birtaniya, ya fallasa duk wani dan sandan Birtaniya da ke cikin 'yan sanda, ya kuma yi wa wani jami'in 'yan sandan kasar babban abin kunya, wanda ya yi wa Kevin Eldon takaici.
Wannan shi ne karshe ga Firayim Minista, wanda yake da biki da kuma damuwa, wanda ke fama da nauyin rashin amincewa da siyasa: Emma Thompson ya yi wannan Teresa-May, amma ba shi da yawa a cikin rubutun da za a yi aiki a kan.
