Menene bikin Global Citizen Festival, kuma ya taimaka wajen rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, bikin New York Global Citizen Festival, wanda ke gudanar da bikin kiɗa na shekara-shekara, tare da gagarumin taron masu shahara, da kuma irin wannan gagarumar manufa: kawar da talauci daga duniya.
Bikin na Global Citizen Festival da aka gudanar a karo na bakwai, zai ga dubun dubatan mutane a yankin Great Law na Central Park, ba wai kawai suna jin dadin masu yin waka kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma suna wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron, wato kawar da matsanancin talauci nan da shekarar 2030.
An fara bikin Global Citizen a shekara ta 2012 kuma ya kasance wani bangare na Global Poverty Project, wani kungiya na kasa da kasa da ke neman kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fama da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta (sai dai idan suna son biyan kuɗin tikitin VIP), masu halartar za su yi ayyuka da yawa ko kuma su ba da kansu, su aika imel ga shugabannin duniya, su kira, ko kuma su yi wani abu mai muhimmanci don su taimaka wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da muradin kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar da Global Citizen ta samu, idan har shekara 12 ke nan kafin ta cimma burinta?
Shin ra'ayin ba da kyauta ne hanya ce ta gaske ta sa mutane su nemi aiki ko kuwa kawai wani tsari ne na dannawa inda mutane ke jin cewa suna yin wani abu mai muhimmanci ta hanyar sanya hannu a kan intanet ko kuma yin amfani da siginar?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ta yi rajistar fiye da aikin miliyan 19 na masu goyon bayanta, suna neman cimma manufofi da dama.
Ya ce, waɗannan ayyuka sun taimaka wa shugabannin duniya su san fiye da dala biliyan 37 na alkawura da manufofi da za su shafi rayukan mutane biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta yi nuni da wajibai 390 da sanarwa da suka samo asali daga ayyukansu, wanda aƙalla dala biliyan 10 aka riga aka biya ko aka ba da kuɗi.
Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa, asusun ajiyar kuɗi ya shafi mutane kusan miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Wasu manyan alkawura sun hada da hadin gwiwar masu zuba jari da masu aiwatarwa na The Power of Nutrition da ke Burtaniya, wanda ke da alhakin "taimakawa yara su samu cikakkiyar damar su", ta hanyar bada dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don taimakawa kasar ta kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki bayan samun fiye da sakonni 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da agaji, gwamnatocin ƙasa da kuma 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya mai da rashin abinci mai gina jiki a matsayin sanarwa ta tarihi game da rashin adalci na zamantakewa", in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan The Power of Nutrition, a wani taron jama'a a London a watan Afrilu na shekarar 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma sanar da cewa bayan fiye da ayyuka 5,000 da suka bukaci inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara a Burtaniya, gwamnati ta sanar da shirin bayar da tallafi na The Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 da ke bukatar taimakon abinci mai gina jiki.
A amsa ga wata KKK a shafinta na yanar gizo, inda aka tambaye ta, "Me ya sa kake ganin za mu iya kawo karshen talauci?"
Global Citizen ta amsa:  Hanya ce mai tsawo da wahala - wani lokacin muna faɗuwa kuma muna kasawa.
Amma yayin da muke fuskantar manyan hakkokin jama'a da kuma motsi na hana wariyar launin fata, muna da tabbacin cewa za mu yi nasara, domin tare muna da iko.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe su ne kawai 'yan wasan da za su yi rawa a wannan shekara a birnin New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman suka shirya.
Amurka na iya amfani da "tafin" sojojin ruwa don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Ministan Cikin Gida
A cewar jaridar Washington Examiner, idan aka bukaci, Washington na iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa wajen hana Rasha shiga kasuwar makamashi, ciki har da yankin Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa, shiga Rasha a Syria, musamman idan ta yi aiki a kan gayyatar da gwamnati ta yi, hujja ce ta binciken sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
'Ina ganin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne domin suna son su yi amfani da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai, a kudancin Turai,' in ji shi.
Kuma jami'in ya ce akwai hanyoyin da za a bi don magance wannan matsalar.
'Amurka tana da wannan damar ta hanyar sojojin ruwanta na tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa suna bude kuma an toshe su idan ya cancanta, don tabbatar da cewa ba a sayar da makamashin su ba,' in ji shi.
Zinka ya yi wannan jawabi ne ga masu halartar taron da ƙungiyar masu amfani da makamashi ta Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya. Ƙungiyar ba ta riba ce, wadda take wakiltar 'muryar masu amfani da makamashi' a Amirka.
Ya tafi ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke bi da Rasha da Iran, ya ce sun yi kama.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki na Iran da Rasha ya fi ko ƙasa da haka, ƙarfafawa da maye gurbin mai", in ji shi, yayin da yake nuna Rasha a matsayin "ƙwarƙwarar ƙwaraƙwara" wacce tattalin arzikinta ya dogara da mai.
Wannan furucin ya zo ne a daidai lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ke da burin kara fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, inda za ta maye gurbin Rasha, wadda ta fi masu amfani da ita a Turai.
Don yin wannan, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta kori aikin samar da bututun mai mai suna Nord Stream 2, wanda Trump ya ce ya mayar da Berlin a matsayin "kurkukun Moscow".
Moscow ta sha jaddada cewa, aikin da ake yi na samar da bututun mai na Nord Stream 2 mai darajar dala biliyan 11, wanda zai ninka na yanzu zuwa murabba'in mita biliyan 110, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya ce, Washington ta yi hamayya da aikin ne saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki, kuma misali ne na rashin adalci.
"Ina ganin mun yarda cewa ba za a iya amfani da makamashi a matsayin hanyar matsa lamba ba kuma ya kamata masu amfani su sami damar zabar masu samar da su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak a wani taro da ya yi da Ministan Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a watan Satumba a Moscow.
Tunanin Amurka ya fuskanci koma baya daga Jamus, wadda ta tabbatar da jajircewarta ga aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, Kungiyar Masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI) ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta guji siyasar makamashi ta EU da yarjejeniyar biyu da aka yi a Berlin da Moscow.
"Zan fuskanci babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI), bayan ganawar da yayi da shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da kuma shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren na tunanin tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa a 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren daga Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa a zaben da za a yi a tsakanin shekara biyu da biyar.
A fadar majalisa ta Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa yana tunanin tsayawa takararsa.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan ya hada da uwargidan shugaban kasa", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
Bayan 6 ga Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari sosai da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ya kuma ba da rahoton cewa Shugaba Donald Trump yana tura kasar nan cikin hanyar da ba ta dace ba.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump zai yi wa dimokiradiyya", in ji shi.
Warren ya yi tsokaci kan Trump da kuma wanda zai tsaya takara a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
A ranar Juma'a, Warren ya ce, "Tabbas, muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin a yi zabe".
Amma, kuri'ar da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis ta nuna cewa mafi yawan masu zabe Warren ba su yi imanin cewa ya kamata ya tsaya takara a 2020.
Wani bincike da aka yi a Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk da Boston Globe ya nuna cewa kashi 58 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata a zabi Sanata ba.
32% sun goyi bayan irin wannan takarar.
Binciken ya nuna goyon baya ga takarar tsohon gwamna Deval Patrick, inda kashi 38 cikin 100 suka goyi bayan takarar da za a iya yi, kuma kashi 48 cikin 100 suka ki.
Sauran manyan sunayen 'yan Democrat da aka tattauna dangane da yiwuwar takarar 2020 sun hada da tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa Joe Biden da Sanata Bernie Sanders na Vermont.
Bayden ya ce zai yanke shawara a watan Janairu, in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press.
