Wani sabon jirgin ruwan Jamus ya sake turawa
A shekarar 2014 ne aka shirya fara amfani da sabon jirgin ruwan jirgin ruwa mai saurin gudu na rundunar sojin Jamus, wanda zai maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwan yakin sanyi, amma ba a kai ga wannan ba sai shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma tsadar kudade, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na kasar.
An dage fara aiki da sabon jirgin saman Baden-Wuerttemberg mai dauke da jiragen ruwa mai saurin gudu Rheinland-Pfalz zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, a cewar wata sanarwa da aka fitar a jaridar Die Zeit.
Ya kamata jirgin ya shiga cikin rundunar a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da ake fuskanta bayan mika shi ba su sa wannan babban aikin ya kasance mai sauƙi ba.
Jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da rundunar ta yi oda a shekarar 2007 za su maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa masu saurin gudu na Bremen.
Ana iya fahimtar cewa suna da manyan bindigogi, da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami da kuma wasu fasahohin ɓoyewa kamar su radar, infrared da kuma rage siginar sauti.
Sauran mahimman damar sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa - sabon jirgin ruwa mai sauri ya kamata ya iya fitar da shi daga tashar tashar jirgin sama har zuwa shekaru biyu.
Amma, jinkiri na dindindin yana nufin cewa jiragen ruwa masu ƙarfi da suke ba wa Jamus damar ƙarfafa ikonta a ƙasashen waje, za su zama tsofaffi kafin a soma amfani da su.
