Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar ta mayar da jirgin bayan da aka karbe shi.
Ba a san dalilin dawowar ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun yi tsokaci kan wasu manyan 'rashin ingantattun kayan aiki da na'urori' da suka sanya jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka yi amfani da shi a cikin aikin yaƙi.
Rashin kayan aikin ya kasance mai mahimmanci saboda jirgin Baden-Württemberg yana sarrafawa ta hanyar ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa kimanin 120 - kawai rabin ma'aikatan tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An kuma gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi mai yawa, wanda ke rage ƙarfinsa kuma yana iyakance ikon sojojin ruwa don ƙara sabbin abubuwa a nan gaba.
