Girgizar ƙasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu, na Indonesia, ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, suna mai cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu na ci gaba da karuwa.
Tun da an katse sadarwa, masu aikin ceto ba su samu wani bayani ba daga yankin Donggala da ke arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5.
An ce an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke kusa da bakin tekun da ke gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, kuma yawan mutanen da ke cikinta ya kai 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da birnin yake bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwarsa, girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka addabe shi.
Gundumar Donggala yanki ne da ya kai kilomita 300 (180 miles) a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin 2017, an kiyasta cewa Regency, yanki ne na lardin, yana da yawan jama'a 299 200.
Kamun kifi da noma sune manyan ayyukan tattalin arziki na lardin Tsakiya Sulawesi, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Har ila yau, ana samun ma'adinan nickel a lardin, wanda ya fi mayar da hankali a Morowali, a gabar tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesiya ta ce a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya addabi Paluyu da Donggalau sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 a Donggala kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya addabi yankin yammacin Donggala, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ke kusa da Tekun Fasifik, kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi girma a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a gaɓar yamma na lardin Aceh, a arewacin Sumatra, a ƙasar Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya addabi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gaɓar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu, girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa yammacin Sumatra.
An kashe ɗarurruwan mutane a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu maso gabashin tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya addabi gaɓar tekun kudu, ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa wani yanki kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai da ke Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, wanda ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa gundumar Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba, wanda ya tunatar da mutane game da mummunan girgizar kasa da tsunami da aka yi a 2004.
Ba a yi tsunami ba a wannan lokacin, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a cikin gine-gine da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesiya, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta halaka dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido su kasance a cikin wani yanayi na ɗan lokaci.
