Sabon bayani game da ruwa: an rage yawan a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani rahoto na baya-bayan nan da Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Dabbobin Daji ta Florida (FWC) ta bayar ya nuna cewa yawan amfanin gona da ke cike da fure a yankin Tampa Bay yana raguwa.
FWC ta ce akwai rahotanni na ci gaba da bunkasa a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma Collier County, wanda ke nuna raguwar yawan.
Ruwa yana da nisan kusan mil 130 (209 km) a gefen tekun daga arewacin gundumar Pinellas zuwa kudancin gundumar Lee.
Ana iya samun gawawwakin a mil 10 daga gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma adadin gawawwakin ya ragu sosai idan aka kwatanta da na makon da ya gabata.
An kuma samu ruwa a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an samu matsakaicin ma'auni a yankin Pinellas County a bakin teku ko kuma a bakin teku, low zuwa high a yankin Hillsborough County a bakin teku, low zuwa high a yankin Manatee County, low zuwa high a yankin Sarasota County a bakin teku da kuma a bakin teku, low zuwa matsakaicin ma'auni a yankin Charlotte County, low zuwa high a yankin Lee County a bakin teku da kuma a yankin High, da kuma low zuwa high a yankin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni daga Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma Collier County game da ciwon numfashi.
A makon da ya gabata, babu wani rahoton da ya nuna cewa akwai wani ciwon numfashi a yammacin Florida.
